OL,3,CHunt for survivors continues in
OL,4,CVenezuela after two deadly earthquakes
OL,6,FThe search for survivors continues
OL,7,Facross cities in northern Venezuela
OL,8,Fafter two earthquakes hit the country
OL,9,Fon Thursday.
OL,11,FOfficials say 235 people were killed
OL,12,Fand at least 4,300 are believed to be
OL,13,Finjured.
OL,15,FThe number of casualties is expected
OL,16,Fto rise as thousands of people have
OL,17,Fbeen reported missing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
