OL,3,CHunt for survivors continues in
OL,4,CVenezuela after two deadly earthquakes
OL,6,FThe 7.2- and 7.5-magnitude earthquakes
OL,7,Fthat hit on Wednesday evening were
OL,8,Famong the strongest in Venezuela in
OL,9,Fmore than a century.
OL,11,FVenezuelan state TV showed images of
OL,12,Frescues, including a woman who was
OL,13,Ftrapped under a cement slab with only
OL,14,Fa bare foot poking out before rescuers
OL,15,Fslid her out alive.
OL,17,FThe coastal region of La Guaira, north
OL,18,Fof the capital Caracas, suffered some
OL,19,Fof the heaviest damage and casualties,
OL,20,Fand it where the main airport is based.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
