OL,3,CHunt for survivors continues in
OL,4,CVenezuela after two deadly earthquakes
OL,6,FIt was closed due to damage, which has
OL,7,Fcomplicated aid efforts.
OL,9,FMany were stunned on Thursday morning
OL,10,Fas they saw buildings had been reduced
OL,11,Fto skeletons, furniture hanging out of
OL,12,Fwindows and helicopters overhead.
OL,13,FBuildings were flattened and streets
OL,14,Fwere cracked open.
OL,16,FFamilies posted missing-person flyers
OL,17,Fwith photos of loved ones while others
OL,18,Fshared handwritten lists of names as
OL,19,Fthey searched.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
