OL,3,CHunt for survivors continues in
OL,4,CVenezuela after two deadly earthquakes
OL,6,FVenezuelans abroad struggled to make
OL,7,Fcontact with relatives due to
OL,8,Finterrupted phone service in the
OL,9,Fcountry.
OL,11,FIn downtown Caracas, hundreds spent
OL,12,Fthe night huddled in parks, parking
OL,13,Flots and other open spaces.
OL,15,FThe natural disaster is the latest
OL,16,Fchallenge for acting President Delcy
OL,17,FRodriguez, the former vice president
OL,18,Fwho took office in January after
OL,19,FNicolas Maduro's capture.
