OL,3,CHunt for survivors continues in
OL,4,CVenezuela after two deadly earthquakes
OL,6,FVenezuela has been facing economic
OL,7,Fdisarray for more than a decade, and
OL,8,Fmany people reject the legitimacy of
OL,9,Fthe political movement Rodriguez
OL,10,Frepresents.
OL,12,FRodriguez declared a state of
OL,13,Femergency in an address to the nation
OL,14,Flate Wednesday. She said the
OL,15,Fgovernment was creating a $200 million
OL,16,F(#151m) reconstruction fund for
OL,17,Fdamaged hospitals and homes.
OL,26,@qD@\rttD@Ert
