OL,3,CHunt for survivors continues in
OL,4,CVenezuela after two deadly earthquakes
OL,6,FShe appealed to businesses on
OL,7,FThursday, asking them to make heavy
OL,8,Fconstruction equipment available for
OL,9,Frescue operations.
OL,11,F"We hope to rescue as many living
OL,12,Fpeople as possible," Rodriguez said.
OL,14,FThe UK government said it is providing
OL,15,F#2 million to help the emergency
OL,16,Fresponse in Venezuela, after the
OL,17,FForeign Office said all its UK staff
OL,18,Fin Venezuela were safe.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@TO]tD@Zrt
