OL,3,CHunt for survivors continues in
OL,4,CVenezuela after two deadly earthquakes
OL,6,FIt added that it had received no
OL,7,Freports of British nationals involved
OL,8,Fin the disaster.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,16,F"We are making immediately available
OL,17,F#2 million of emergency humanitarian
OL,18,Fassistance, so that we can get search
OL,19,Fand rescue teams into Venezuela, so
OL,20,Fthat we can do full assessments of the
OL,21,Fdamage that's been done.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
