OL,3,CHunt for survivors continues in
OL,4,CVenezuela after two deadly earthquakes
OL,6,F"We're also working with the United
OL,7,FStates, with Canada, with the United
OL,8,FNations, and making sure that we can
OL,9,Fget support in for Venezuela, for the
OL,10,Fpeople who need our help."
OL,12,FAny Britons requiring assistance are
OL,13,Fadvised to follow the advice of local
OL,14,Fauthorities and contact +58 (0) 212
OL,15,F263 8411 from Venezuela and 0207 008
OL,16,F5000 from the UK if they require
OL,17,Furgent assistance.
OL,19,FMexico, Qatar, Brazil, Spain, Portugal
OL,20,Fand Canada were among countries which
OL,21,Fsaid they would send aid to Venezuela.
