OL,3,CHunt for survivors continues in
OL,4,CVenezuela after two deadly earthquakes
OL,6,FUS Secretary of State Marco Rubio
OL,7,Fconfirmed the US was "immediately"
OL,8,Fdeploying search and rescue teams and
OL,9,Fmedical resources, while on Thursday
OL,10,Fthe US Treasury suspended some
OL,11,Fsanctions to help relief efforts.
